channel.title: Help with Ultimatum 718 source
channel.description:
I downloaded it to try out everything works well maybe rip some stuff but i can compile any changes i made >.> i looked and it looks like some files are missing? Did anyone else have this problem or can someone send me these files, heres the error im receiving.
[code]starting... src\com\rs\game\player\content\grandexchange\GrandExchangeLoader.java:14: error: package com.google.gson does not exist import com.google.gson.Gson; ^ src\com\rs\game\player\content\grandexchange\GrandExchangeLoader.java:15: error: package com.google.gson does not exist import com.google.gson.GsonBuilder; ^ src\com\rs\game\player\content\grandexchange\GrandExchangeLoader.java:16: error: package com.google.gson.reflect does not exist import com.google.gson.reflect.TypeToken; ^ src\com\rs\game\player\content\grandexchange\GrandExchangeLoader.java:138: error : cannot find symbol private static Gson gson = new GsonBuilder().setPrettyPrinting().create( ); ^ symbol: class Gson location: class GrandExchangeLoader src\com\rs\game\npc\combat\impl\RosDharokCombat.java:3: error: package com.npcn does not exist import com.npcn.NulledNpc; ^ src\com\rs\game\player\content\grandexchange\GrandExchangeLoader.java:104: error : cannot find symbol new TypeToken<List<GrandExchangeOffer>>() { ^ symbol: class TypeToken location: class GrandExchangeLoader src\com\rs\game\player\content\grandexchange\GrandExchangeLoader.java:138: error : cannot find symbol private static Gson gson = new GsonBuilder().setPrettyPrinting().create( ); ^ symbol: class GsonBuilder location: class GrandExchangeLoader src\com\rs\game\npc\combat\impl\RosDharokCombat.java:17: error: cannot find symb ol return new Object[] { new NulledNpc(2026).GetNulledId() }; ^ symbol: class NulledNpc location: class RosDharokCombat Note: src\com\rs\game\map\MapBuilder.java uses unchecked or unsafe operations. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:unchecked for details. 8 errors Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
Looks like the files im missing ( i cant find on google) are Gson.java , GsonBuilder.java , TypeToken.java , NulledNpc.java , and thats all :s
